 - LoKi/WrongMass.h, src/WrongMass.cpp
   few useful functions LoKi::Kinematics::WorngMass, which 
   allows to use "wrong" mass hypothesis for 
   evaluation of kinematical quantities.
 
   const LHCb::Particle* p1 = ... ; 
   const LHCb::Particle* p2 = ... ;
  
   // evaluate the invariant mass using the muon hypotheses:
   const double mass =  
      LoKi::Kinematics::wrongMass ( p1->momentum() , "mu+" , 
                                    p2->momentum() , "mu-" ) ;


